OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1964FThe first edition of Newsroom
OL,7,Fairs on BBC Two.
OL,8,
OL,9,FPresented by Gerald Priestland. The
OL,10,Fprogramme is broadcast from Alexandra
OL,11,FPalace due to a power cut, which
OL,12,Fdisrupted the official launch (of the
OL,13,Fprogramme and channel) from TV Centre.
OL,14,FRichard Baker, from Alexandra Palace,
OL,15,Flinked together programmes for BBC One.
OL,16,
OL,17,FNewsroom introduced the idea of
OL,18,F"in-depth reporting" and the presenters
OL,19,Fwere taken from the reporting staff.
OL,20,FThe programme had a more informal
OL,21,Fpresentation style, with presenters
OL,22,Fwearing pullovers, in contrast to the
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
